/*! \page keyboardReference Keyboard reference

Default keyboard settings are:

LMB - select single unit
LMB (hold) - activate rubber band selection
LMB (flick) - move around the map
Ctrl + LMB - select multiple units
Ctrl + [digit] - create a unit group
[digit] - select a previously created unit group

T - toggle top menu
G - toggle bottom menu

P - pause
S - cancel order (stop)
F - follow unit
R - move fast (run)
M - move
N - sneak
A - attack
K - smoke
D - defend
B - ambush

Developer controls (not adjustable in config):
] - swap map background image with hipsometric image
[ - toggle player's side
*/